This paper deals with the capacity region of a UAV-enabled two-user broadcast channel, which involves wireless communication and optimization of UAV trajectory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves networked systems and control, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the second likely category. The paper also involves optimization and control of UAVs, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the third likely category. The paper also involves robotics and autonomous systems, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics) as the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper involves machine learning and optimization, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the fifth likely category.
